      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (4.2 M, 11.7 M, 31.4 M cells) yields a GCI of 3.8% for the normalised hemolysis index at the nominal operating point (5 L/min, 2800 RPM), satisfying the acceptance criterion."
