      "rationale": "Six uncertain inputs (Carreau-Yasuda parameters α, n, λ; haematocrit; inlet velocity profile shape parameter; hemolysis model exponent) are assigned distributions from literature meta-analysis and propagated via 500-sample Monte Carlo, yielding 95% credible intervals on NIH."
